        public Gardening(String invoiceID,
                 String propertyAddress,
                 PropertySizeEnum propertySize,
                 Boolean scheduledMonthly,
                 Integer numberOfServices,
                 Integer numberOfFloors,
                 Integer month)
        Constructs a Gardening service with the give parameters.
        Parameters:
        invoiceID - the invoiceID of the gardening service
        propertyAddress - the property address of the house/place getting a Gardening service
        propertySize - the property size represented as an Enum (SMALL, MEDIUM, LARGE)
        scheduledMonthly - a Boolean value checking if the service is monthly or a 1 time service
        numberOfFloors - the number of floors the scheduled property has
        numberOfServices - the number of Gardening servies the property has had in the past
        month - the month scheduled for the Gardening service
